asukotelin/shirotelin\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">shirotelin</a>, it is perfect! I don't feel blind anymore!</p>\n<p><img class=\"g-image g-image--lazy g-image--loading\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3csvg fill='none' viewBox='0 0 1427 423' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' xmlns:xlink='http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink'%3e%3cdefs%3e%3cfilter id='__svg-blur-c29f27cf0d593cb9e53990a9373365fa'%3e%3cfeGaussianBlur in='SourceGraphic' stdDeviation='40'/%3e%3c/filter%3e%3c/defs%3e%3cimage x='0' y='0' filter='url(%23__svg-blur-c29f27cf0d593cb9e53990a9373365fa)' width='1427' height='423' xlink:href='data:image/png%3bbase64%2ciVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAEAAAAATCAYAAAAgcwuHAAAACXBIWXMAAAsSAAALEgHS3X78AAAFMElEQVRYw%2bVYiY7jNgzN/39e0W7nzGXHdnzJ9ymHfY9KdpPMDDAo2p0taoAQRVESRZF8SlZFWkn8EEu6P8owDDIvs8x2Fgua5%2bmGpsm11jq6H7%2bWX3ira73VvdW5lXGfcRz/deI%2bq64bJM9K6dJepmqWsZylLwcxppOmWaTvF6lrK21r4aBF2xI6JMrrxkLPStctUmI%2bSeVnMqaBbNJxEnW5Tj84/epMbg8nmyYrl%2b90kpvvvv/h90m9VdN0kqVGuqiXMZtkiEZpw07ipJE0W/SAeTGLqXDI4aR8Ar04nSTLJylKKwn4HHyislkpTpwsz0s5xr3khodc0Fo9cIn1jvGEPWbo0FFW5x3CAU6f5Gd9q74fZY/wPyYGBzPiByEI/WMq3iGQeJNJtaskfzKSrwspdqU0%2b0ay11z2XirrTSUposfzW9lC7xA0stvX4h/Yr0GtxDhoklSgVLZbT4qilCA8whEVDp1LGEZyOISSZTnmBVjPyOt6D4fmWN/D2FHCKFGbttsD1g8kQt8UlWw2PuwPsF4sQRDLZudL6hvJng3sM7BnhNMnrNuDHyA7t36vF7iaplmiY4fDdrgNZxAXOcZwgB/KZu1J6McS%2bYkE3lG8bSBFWoq3C2F4DEMPMCaF0SUMi2BMpLIUabWB7noTyLIIaNF6MI4D/O74ZbHC/YdhVLrw82wRBYP22Y7jpPyInL30Sdbaq7lO1rOOIYXm3qXSOC5Y76Qtiel34ed5YQ3opcxrGVIsgrDsYxQI3JiJa0TFgFxHyNYuDUgRxlN4LjMM8xEpsuBmz%2bGv4Yx0YZqkk8pdGky4oQE379IjjAZNiTSj8bN85acOKJJamqiVLkHhC1tpglaqtEF%2b44D1jOJlwbvCx3ByRetMjZNrMTvLWOhcfZiUJ6VwcNPaH/rQMwYOGOdzcTt9Ca0Mbr9BClRH5HeQSxkZqZPyp97CVx1eHZCmhdQoWGM9SgfIKgIjbY4oyGqpolLb098wclnuZXJFp%2b/ttROu24/lpzdYd61zv%2bY13a%2bpKZBlBUK/lwVFYWoBgVkjFjDUl530eAv0RfeP3PK1Qz4y%2bl7Gwvme/L2Dcf03B/8g0q75VVnWEkSxvLzuZQs4eQb8HACDOy8AGhzk2%2bOrws7D4xo6O1kDFch7fiR/PqxBr4oCnhcp//i0keeXnfI%2b4OsBOn98ewEUZkCWTNciZXkBWMsASyGKodHxBPDH%2bU/PW5UR5jjuHyIgTqIwxzW4